</div>

### \`druid_button.set_click_zone(zone: Opaque<"node"> | string | undefined): druid_button\`

<div class="api-symbol-body">

Set additional button click area.
Useful to restrict click outside of stencil node or scrollable content.
If button node placed inside stencil node, it will be automatically set to this stencil node.

**Parameters**

- \`zone\`:тАВ\`Opaque<"node"> | string | undefined\` тАФ Gui node

**Returns**

- \`druid_button\` тАФ The current button instance

</div>

### \`druid_button.set_key_trigger(key: Hash | string): druid_button\`

<div class="api-symbol-body">

Set key name to trigger this button by keyboard.

**Parameters**

- \`key\`:тАВ\`Hash | string\` тАФ The action_id of the input key. Example: "key_space"

**Returns**

- \`druid_button\` тАФ The current button instance

</div>

### \`druid_button.get_key_trigger(): Hash\`

<div class="api-symbol-body">

