</div>

### \`druid_button.set_check_function(check_function: unknown | undefined, failure_callback: unknown | undefined): druid_button\`

<div class="api-symbol-body">

Set function for additional check for button click availability.

**Parameters**

- \`check_function\`:тАВ\`unknown | undefined\` тАФ Should return true or false. If true - button can be pressed.
- \`failure_callback\`:тАВ\`unknown | undefined\` тАФ Function will be called on button click, if check function returns false

**Returns**

- \`druid_button\` тАФ The current button instance

</div>

### \`druid_button.set_web_user_interaction(is_web_mode: boolean | undefined): druid_button\`

<div class="api-symbol-body">

Set Button mode to work inside user HTML5 interaction event.

It's required to make protected things like copy & paste text, show mobile keyboard, etc
The HTML5 button doesn't call any events except on_click event.

If the game is not HTML, html mode will be not enabled

**Parameters**

- \`is_web_mode\`:тАВ\`boolean | undefined\` тАФ If true - button will be called inside html5 callback

**Returns**

- \`druid_button\` тАФ The current button instance

</div>

