<div class="api-symbol-body">

Multiplier for inertion speed. Default: 30

</div>

### \`druid_scroll_style.POINTS_DEADZONE: number | undefined\`

<div class="api-symbol-body">

Speed to check points of interests in no_inertion mode. Default: 20

</div>

### \`druid_scroll_style.BACK_SPEED: number | undefined\`

<div class="api-symbol-body">

Scroll back returning lerp speed. Default: 35

</div>

### \`druid_scroll_style.ANIM_SPEED: number | undefined\`

<div class="api-symbol-body">

Scroll gui.animation speed for scroll_to function. Default: 2

</div>

### \`druid_scroll_style.EXTRA_STRETCH_SIZE: number | undefined\`

<div class="api-symbol-body">

extra size in pixels outside of scroll (stretch effect). Default: 0

</div>

### \`druid_scroll_style.SMALL_CONTENT_SCROLL: boolean | undefined\`

