### \`druid_rich_text.set_text(text: string | undefined): LuaMultiReturn<[druid_rich_text_word[], druid_rich_text_lines_metrics]>\`

<div class="api-symbol-body">

Set text for Rich Text
-- Color
rich_text:set_text("я╝Ьcolor=redя╝ЮFoobarя╝Ь/colorя╝Ю")
rich_text:set_text("я╝Ьcolor=1.0,0,0,1.0я╝ЮFoobarя╝Ь/colorя╝Ю")
rich_text:set_text("я╝Ьcolor=#ff0000я╝ЮFoobarя╝Ь/colorя╝Ю")
rich_text:set_text("я╝Ьcolor=#ff0000ffя╝ЮFoobarя╝Ь/colorя╝Ю")
-- Shadow
rich_text:set_text("я╝Ьshadow=redя╝ЮFoobarя╝Ь/shadowя╝Ю")
rich_text:set_text("я╝Ьshadow=1.0,0,0,1.0я╝ЮFoobarя╝Ь/shadowя╝Ю")
rich_text:set_text("я╝Ьshadow=#ff0000я╝ЮFoobarя╝Ь/shadowя╝Ю")
rich_text:set_text("я╝Ьshadow=#ff0000ffя╝ЮFoobarя╝Ь/shadowя╝Ю")
-- Outline
rich_text:set_text("я╝Ьoutline=redя╝ЮFoobarя╝Ь/outlineя╝Ю")
rich_text:set_text("я╝Ьoutline=1.0,0,0,1.0я╝ЮFoobarя╝Ь/outlineя╝Ю")
rich_text:set_text("я╝Ьoutline=#ff0000я╝ЮFoobarя╝Ь/outlineя╝Ю")
rich_text:set_text("я╝Ьoutline=#ff0000ffя╝ЮFoobarя╝Ь/outlineя╝Ю")
-- Font
rich_text:set_text("я╝Ьfont=MyCoolFontя╝ЮFoobarя╝Ь/fontя╝Ю")
-- Size
rich_text:set_text("я╝Ьsize=2я╝ЮTwice as largeя╝Ь/sizeя╝Ю")
-- Line break
rich_text:set_text("я╝Ьbr/я╝ЮInsert a line break")
-- No break
rich_text:set_text("я╝Ьnobrя╝ЮPrevent the text from breaking")
-- Image
rich_text:set_text("я╝Ьimg=texture:imageя╝ЮDisplay image")
rich_text:set_text("я╝Ьimg=texture:image,sizeя╝ЮDisplay image with size")
rich_text:set_text("я╝Ьimg=texture:image,width,heightя╝ЮDisplay image with width and height")

**Parameters**

- \`text\`:тАВ\`string | undefined\` тАФ The text to set

**Returns**

- \`druid_rich_text_word[]\`
- \`druid_rich_text_lines_metrics\`

</div>

