<div class="api-symbol-body">

Call this in gui_script on_input function.

**Parameters**

- \`action_id\`:тАВ\`Hash\` тАФ Action_id from on_input
- \`action\`:тАВ\`LuaTable\` тАФ Action from on_input

**Returns**

